% gen337: definitional teaching (mode=define) — the CAPTURE frame that makes any
% concept teachable by prompt: «learn the definition of X: "…"» asserts
% concept(X, "…") into the session; the consumer (kb_concept_def and the what-is
% path) already read any pred(Key, "Description"). Comprehension = knowledge:
% a new phrasing of this frame is another learnable row, never C.
